{"type": "article", "id": 18867, "title": "薯片和果酱包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-11T08:52:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153740z42KUlS95avQLTfj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t食品包装设计常常用鲜艳的颜色，但德克萨斯的 tortilla chips and salsa 却走了干净素雅的风格。设计来自美国的包装设计工作室 Farm Design ，薯片和果酱都使用了白色做主要背景，搭配黑色的文字，有手绘的小麦、洋葱和玉米或水果的图案，很文艺。在花花绿绿的食品包装里也是脱颖而出的办法。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061537384FNfSRWjIGEcCBVh.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153739svT8jGif60hq9nmd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.26574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153739Rcqx9UinNs0XaoJk.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.56574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061537402OtFWghbXeZAuQT0.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5287037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}